runtime/logs/task-point-state-machine-resolution-discuss-point-codex-yolo-openai-gpt-5.5.log:1497:./runtime/logs/task-point-state-machine-resolution-propose-solutions-codex-yolo-openai-gpt-5.5.log:244:./runtime/logs/task-point-inbox-hierarchy-propose-solutions-codex-yolo-openai-gpt-5.5.log:157:  - Constraints: The lookup order must avoid conflicts; explicit overrides, rhei-local declarations, inherited `index.panta.md` defaults, and built-in fallback must each have a defined precedence; omitted `**States:**` on a rhei may inherit a project default.
