runtime/logs/task-point-state-machine-resolution-discuss-point-codex-yolo-openai-gpt-5.5.log:1499:./runtime/logs/task-point-state-machine-resolution-propose-solutions-codex-yolo-openai-gpt-5.5.log:246:./runtime/logs/task-point-inbox-hierarchy-propose-solutions-codex-yolo-openai-gpt-5.5.log:315:/home/vjovanov/f/rhei/skills/rhei-state-machine-writer/SKILL.md:8:Design a custom Rhei state machine only when the built-in `rhei` workflow is too generic. Produce a YAML file matching the project's real phases, actors, gates, retries, and automation hooks, ready to be referenced by a plan's `**States:**` declaration. The state machine writer runs before the plan writer: it defines the workflow the plan later uses.
